---
title: Frank's RedHot Sizzling Chicken Salad with Charred Sweetcorn and Feta
description: Make your salad sing with our Frank's Sizzling Chicken Salad. Enjoy the taste sensations of charred sweetcorn mixed with the creamy saltiness of feta cheese, refreshing baby gem lettuce and juicy tomatoes. Topped with chicken thighs in Frank's RedHot sauce, it's a sizzling salad everyone will want to try.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/franks-chicken-salad-6f63aa42-ebe0a7e5.jpg
